dc:description: Colorless with green tinge.  Broken and mended.  Crizzling and milky weathering.  Material fair.  Pinprick bubbles.  Sandy and black impurities.  Unworked rim, slightly outsplayed.  Conical shape.  Straight sides tapering downward.  Two groups of three lines of wheel incisions below rim and just above the middle.  Solid pointed base.
